    "summary": "A dedicated and enthusiastic professional with broad experience in business management,  strategic  business transformation, communications and operations. I currently work as Corporate Sustainability & Climate Change leader in ERM, an  international consulting company, with a focus on digitalization, sustainability and low carbon energy transitions. ERM offers end to end strategic and technical advice on sustainability and decarbonization roadmaps and implementation. My previous role was as . Global Change Management Director for strategic business transformation, change management, engagement, learning and design solutions. With a growing team of international consultants, we provide our broad customer base a single source for change-related and employee engagement services during strategic business transitions: - change impact assessment, risk assessment and mitigation, change journey mapping, internal communications strategy and implementation, innovative design, blended learning and change management execution. Check www.erm.com. Clients include large corporations such as Shell, Syngenta, Repsol Sinopec, Sika, Airbus, BP, Solvay.\n\nPreviously, I worked as a corporate communications advisor for EMEA region at Intergraph Process, Power & Marine (now Hexagon), the leading global provider of engineering software for plant design, plant automation, 3D plant modelling & visualization. \n\nI hold an MBA with a focus on organizational change and minors in Innovation and Entrepreneurship. I love working at an international environment and enjoy multifunctional positions where strategic thinking, innovation and project management are required. I very much enjoy dealing with transformation\u2019 processes related to business transitions, risk management, strategic innovation and corporate responsibility. I am an analytical and solution-oriented person, able to grasp sensitive situations and to foresee and plan quick responses. \n\nOther clients include steel manufacturing company Tata Steel, insurance company Aegon, mining company BHP Billiton, satellite company World Skies and the European intelligence organization, Europol. I have managed a client portfolio of large international matrix companies, large professional teams and budgets.\n\n*Strategic management\n*Change management\n*Innovation\n*Employee engagement\n*Project management & execution\n*Stakeholder relations\n*Media relations\n*Reputation management",
